Value Required,Filldown NAME (\S.*?)
Value Filldown TYPE (\S+)
Value Filldown DESCRIPTION (.*)
Value Filldown ITEMS (\d+)
Value Filldown REFERENCE (\d+)
Value List INDEX (\d+)
Value List ADDRESS (.+)

Start
  ^Address-set: -> Continue.Record
  ^Address-set:\s+${NAME} 
  ^Type:\s+${TYPE}
  ^Description:\s+${DESCRIPTION}
  ^Item number\(s\):\s+${ITEMS}
  ^Reference number\(s\):\s+${REFERENCE}
  ^\s+address\s+${INDEX}\s+${ADDRESS}
  ^Address-set:\s+${NAME} -> Record Start
  ^\s*$$